# demos/chat.tape — Basic chat with markdown rendering
Output demos/chat.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "hello"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "what is the eisenhower matrix?"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Type "give me a quick python fizzbuzz"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "exit"
Enter
